Let me think about this differently. The issue is that when the page first renders, `goalsExpanded` is an empty Set, so no items are expanded. When a user clicks an item, `goalsExpanded` gets that index. Then clicking again removes it.

So on first render, all items have `goals-item-body hidden` (collapsed). When user clicks, it becomes `goals-item-body` (expanded) with animation.

